title: One Step Beyond 1x10 and 2x17 [retr?tv]
description:
One Step Beyond (1959)

1x10. The Vision   3/24/1959 
In the trenches in WWI, soldiers as usual are dying like flies as expected. All of a sudden the French troops drop their arms and walk serenely away from the front. They are charged with the capital crime of dissertion, but they are not the only soldiers who walked away from the fighting that day.
  Guest star: Jean Del Val (French Soldier), Bruce Gordon (Captain Emil Tremaine), Richard Devon (Major Lamarr), Pernell Roberts (Sergeant Vy), H.M. Wynant (Private Lacoste), Peter Miles (II) (Private Marsee), Jerry Oddo (Private Mollene), Will J. White (German Soldier), Rene Korper (Boy)

2x17. Earthquake   1/12/1960    
The story of the bellhop who foretold The Great San Francisco Earthquake of 1906
  Guest star: David Opatoshu (Gerald Perkins), Elvira Curci (Rosa Bandetti), Martin Garralaga (Carlo Bandetti), Olan Soule (Harris), Harry Ellerbe (Mr. Adams), Oliver McGowan (Mr. Stevens), Nora Marlowe, Wayne Mallory, Steve Fenton, Gregg Stewart, Herb Vigran (Grocery Wagon Driver)
